{"tid":581244,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖] 獨遊比利時五天遊記","createTime":"2018-03-05T07:24:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T10:27:01.000Z","uid":137715,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"fdd29481abf5150ede083d1133bcd813c2838768","tid":581244,"uid":137715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T07:24:30.000Z","msg":"見返新工前有個幾禮拜空檔，心血來潮自己去咗比利時五日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大學grad trip去過一次歐遊，去咗成個月，啲大路國家都去過哂，所以今次揀個有新鮮感嘅地方。<br />\n<br />\n其實都知三月開始有直航，啲時間仲要幾靚，不過返咗新工唔知幾時先可以請假，所以都係早走早著算吧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今次經倫敦轉機，雖然飛過去嗰程只係個幾鐘，但前前後後就少大半朝玩喇。<br />\n<br />\n呢五日去咗三個地方，「歐洲首都」布魯塞爾 (Brussels)、布魯日 (Bruges)同根特 (Ghent)，三個地方都有截然不同嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7daa740f5d0fd8a46a872b90a452fbe93501d21a","tid":581244,"uid":131731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T07:31:59.000Z","msg":"Exchange果陣去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲薯條好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48acce2fdb1757d9636faac3042617b8dfab54be","tid":581244,"uid":137715,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T07:45:25.000Z","msg":"布魯塞爾係歐洲典型嘅首都大城市，佢個布魯塞爾大廣場 (Grand Place)勁近中央車站，夜晚著哂燈又真係好靚。今次住正喺嗰度，酒店隔離有個勁大隻嘅藍精靈雕像，見到先知原來藍精靈係布魯塞爾漫畫家嘅創作嚟。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/153838_e68af58f3a03e1616adbfe07b763ff46.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F153838_e68af58f3a03e1616adbfe07b763ff46.JPG&h=8ddf93ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/153842_c429385626f95cab68271b23663bc76e.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F153842_c429385626f95cab68271b23663bc76e.JPG&h=47e0384e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/153840_f90cf5b76d6f5b536012f8c48d6f1b1e.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F153840_f90cf5b76d6f5b536012f8c48d6f1b1e.JPG&h=31c59814&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae05e04899903329339ae985eca322335e4e7909","tid":581244,"uid":137715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T07:46:09.000Z","msg":"仆街，唔知點解up 唔到圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 整一整先"},{"pid":"3121849c1e2d24061456bbfb3e7395e9bc95ec2c","tid":581244,"uid":137715,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T08:07:32.000Z","msg":"廿步距離內有個Galeries Royales Saint-Hubert購物廊，係買手信嘅好地方，兩邊有好多比利時朱古力牌子，多到都唔知點揀，不過入到去多數都有得試食，試啱先買。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/160059_da1f64b54297434ef6321aa54aa4cb89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F160059_da1f64b54297434ef6321aa54aa4cb89.jpg&h=9e1fc88a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/160056_5c0840ce6c0766c15b15b361358de457.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F160056_5c0840ce6c0766c15b15b361358de457.jpg&h=ea97abec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/160057_dc73f5b96c118627a81444c020eb5872.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F160057_dc73f5b96c118627a81444c020eb5872.jpg&h=d5182ede&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/160057_e08e5ce46734ec8ee410f6f8bc758317.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F160057_e08e5ce46734ec8ee410f6f8bc758317.jpg&h=891d8f21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/160058_880ba4d473650ff01b00320423f8bb32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F160058_880ba4d473650ff01b00320423f8bb32.jpg&h=77ddeb18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他景點都係步行距離，好似尿尿小童咁都係好快見到。不過個細路比想像中細隻好多，經過見到有堆人圍住先至留意到。沿路一路行仲可以掃街食埋嗰度嘅名物：窩夫、薯條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/160145_4064c8b100c756701e15f0c788b60c8f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F160145_4064c8b100c756701e15f0c788b60c8f.jpg&h=28e05e06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/160144_d9de599717c74ccb4ebff016358bebb8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F160144_d9de599717c74ccb4ebff016358bebb8.jpg&h=41f8a5b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/160144_8520fe99a729548138a845c400d4c937.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F160144_8520fe99a729548138a845c400d4c937.jpg&h=18194745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/160145_a285a815bd2f5ade1c756f09581ca7b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F160145_a285a815bd2f5ade1c756f09581ca7b9.jpg&h=86ed4451&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n布魯塞爾叫得做「歐洲首都」，係因為嗰度集結哂四大主要歐盟機構，其中三個更加係總部嘅所在地。我就入咗唯獨唔係總部嘅歐洲議會參觀，有英文導賞，幾值得一睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/160205_6c307a3e7ea9b8e812d29d341f3494a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F160205_6c307a3e7ea9b8e812d29d341f3494a4.jpg&h=b58960d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/160206_2874b158efda48e11854ad65c32e6bbb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F160206_2874b158efda48e11854ad65c32e6bbb.jpg&h=5fe9a9e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/160206_f175d9c361eee68cdb2e3fa4a6309eb8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F160206_f175d9c361eee68cdb2e3fa4a6309eb8.jpg&h=51871a03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係歐洲議會出面有d 美食市集，都見到幾多係個到返工嘅人買Lunch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/160204_0f3e0243401d5b71a9d021f26b7be6b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F160204_0f3e0243401d5b71a9d021f26b7be6b1.jpg&h=01af878c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/160204_b64aa71df1b033ae5935f8f848624302.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F160204_b64aa71df1b033ae5935f8f848624302.jpg&h=971739f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/160205_8198b9c909ff4e88fc65cdaabfa45569.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F160205_8198b9c909ff4e88fc65cdaabfa45569.jpg&h=3457acdb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f7b5ad40160a1f100c00b1953b45bebfe57f9641","tid":581244,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T08:09:21.000Z","msg":"Bruges同Gent真係幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55b1a6f524226465ed11a0abb59222b2eb5fd2e5","tid":581244,"uid":52707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T08:12:59.000Z","msg":"留名 黎緊六月有一個禮拜留係英國 搵緊地方去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e7182e57dc96a2b1ae8d354be49fb3fef1b9ae","tid":581244,"uid":154196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T08:15:17.000Z","msg":"囡囡相please<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8c7de74218d9b6637357be4b8d824110a451020","tid":581244,"uid":74897,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T08:21:32.000Z","msg":"香港去歐洲玩五日only? 好似有d浪費錢<br />\n在比利時念過一年書 喜歡比利時"},{"pid":"0f4b628e789d79728ce932996ceba8817c757b51","tid":581244,"uid":137715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7daa740f5d0fd8a46a872b90a452fbe93501d21a","tid":581244,"uid":131731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T07:31:59.000Z","msg":"Exchange果陣去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲薯條好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T08:52:30.000Z","msg":"講起又想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"000e1559ea68297b160e4d218f812395cb6281ba","tid":581244,"uid":137715,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T09:17:02.000Z","msg":"玩完兩日布魯塞爾就坐個零鐘火車去布魯日，呢個運河城市有個朵叫「北方威尼斯」，運河上有好多橋，沿住運河行個感覺都幾舒服。可惜我去嗰陣太凍無得坐觀光小船，而家三月份應該就有返喇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個水鄉前身係中世紀古城嚟，建築主要係哥德式，都有唔少幾壯觀嘅建築同教堂。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/171522_28f4a6fef18166340722a876580b94ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F171522_28f4a6fef18166340722a876580b94ee.jpg&h=9e2501d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/171127_0d62be027d4412628c2d7f29b073051b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F171127_0d62be027d4412628c2d7f29b073051b.JPG&h=c8228b92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/171119_4585ed4d2280d368490fd4d0715daaaf.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F171119_4585ed4d2280d368490fd4d0715daaaf.JPG&h=0ed371aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/171121_2626033c57451f0b5aedf6d33b662327.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F171121_2626033c57451f0b5aedf6d33b662327.JPG&h=7159343e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/171124_fa00ced228bb0872ddbdbdf443339c40.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F171124_fa00ced228bb0872ddbdbdf443339c40.JPG&h=219323a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/171128_e42d24cda6505e96a0bcdfcb91b79f1f.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F171128_e42d24cda6505e96a0bcdfcb91b79f1f.JPG&h=d74a07e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其中最出名嘅係聖母大教堂 (Church of Our Lady)，入面有Michelangelo嘅聖母及聖子白色大理石雕塑。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/171250_b58327fd98b545200e74f7b5ea5467c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F171250_b58327fd98b545200e74f7b5ea5467c6.jpg&h=97c46424&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/171249_02c942ab030d083d5ff52b908bf727b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F171249_02c942ab030d083d5ff52b908bf727b9.jpg&h=3e71d59e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/171248_8451332cccb9b877d1340bda39eed3e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F171248_8451332cccb9b877d1340bda39eed3e6.jpg&h=54b9eb8a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"103ef5ba5bbe87bd32a49b0ecc24c6ec995dc231","tid":581244,"uid":137715,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T09:23:59.000Z","msg":"睇完教堂就去咗參觀半月啤酒廠 (De Halve Maan Brewery)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/171805_324eda81bb264b5f57881d8cb78be801.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F171805_324eda81bb264b5f57881d8cb78be801.jpg&h=4cab1326&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/171802_604f2e0915a8c3f77f9208cef6635df5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F171802_604f2e0915a8c3f77f9208cef6635df5.jpg&h=a590ca6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去之前上網買咗飛，有英語導賞團，主要都係了解比利時啤酒歷史同釀酒過程。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/171803_0a7d50a4b337bee250e411a26c235958.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F171803_0a7d50a4b337bee250e411a26c235958.jpg&h=abb2b359&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/171804_a9c2ee4dc64729bbacd886b421b7ed7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F171804_a9c2ee4dc64729bbacd886b421b7ed7e.jpg&h=c7fa2596&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/171804_2706e91d78f478273c27c5f2f93b22f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F171804_2706e91d78f478273c27c5f2f93b22f7.jpg&h=72e0d2d2&s={SIZE}\" 